The GTR committee issued a press release on how to enter: •Sign up on the website www.gtr.co.za, select your distance and pay the registration fee. •You will be allowed to complete your run/cycle any time between the 1st of August to the 22nd of August 2020. •You have to complete the total distance they entered for in one-go. •After the virtual race, runners post their times online and will then receive their virtual medal & Certificate. •There are real medals and one of a kind buffs available to purchase. •There are different packages to choose from. •ASA & CSA Race Rules will apply. Entries remain open until 21 August.